                                <ul>
                                    <li class="active"><a href="student_edu_list.html">학생교육 정보</a></li>
                                    <li><a href="instructor_list.html">교관 관리</a></li>
                                </ul>
                            </nav>
                        </div>
                        <div class="breadcrumb">
                            <ol>
                                <li><i class="icon-breadcrumb-home"></i></li>
